Teresa Maxwell-Conover https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Teresa_Maxwell-Conover 0 Teresa Maxwell-Conover (September 26, 1884 – September 1968) was an actress in Broadway productions in the early 20th century. She was in motion pictures until the early 1940s. She was from Louisville, Kentucky.
